<!--start working area  -->

<h1><center>ELIGIBILITY</center></h1>

<h3><center>WHO CAN PURCHASE AN OLIP POLICY?</center></h3>

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;"> Anyone who is earning  income through a  legal job, is eligible. They can opt for OLIP policies.</p>


 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who is earning income through a public sector or private sector legal job, is eligible. both can opt for OLIP policies, without any difference.</p>
 

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who has purchased a policy can continue with the policy even after the job, untill he/she is capable of paying the pemium amount.</p>

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who is a resident of Pakistan can purchase the Policy.</p>

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who is 18 years of age on the current date can purchase a policy</p>

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who has a national identitiy card can purchase a policy</p>
 
 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who has not purchased an OLIP policy yet, can purchase a policy</p>
 
<h3><center>WHO CAN NOT PURCHASE AN OLIP POLICY?</center></h3>

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;"> Anyone who is not earning  income through a  legal job. They can not opt for OLIP policies.</p>

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who is not earning income are job less or still studying, they can not purchase a policy.</p>
 
 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who is not a resident of Pakistan can not purchase the Policy.</p>

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who is below 18 years of age on the current date can not purchase a policy</p>
 
  <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who is above 60 years of age on the current date can not purchase a policy</p>
  
 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who does not have a valid national identitiy card can not purchase a policy</p>

 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who is a resident of Pakistan, but has dual nationality, can not purchase the Policy.</p>
 
 <p style="margin-left:250px; margin-right:250px; color:#009; font-size:14px;">Anyone who has already purchased a policy, can not purchase the 2nd Policy.</p>



<!--End working area  -->
